le=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384200/extras/ca38144cc7a0e6c06dc65b7d35bae02a.poster.avif?t=1762783541\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384200/extras/ca38144cc7a0e6c06dc65b7d35bae02a.webm?t=1762783541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384200/extras/ca38144cc7a0e6c06dc65b7d35bae02a.mp4?t=1762783541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GLOBAL LEADER BOARD:</strong> Forget good cop/bad cop, remove your shades and set your sights on becoming the best cop! As the tensions rises, so does your score. Do you have what it takes to be awesome?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384200/extras/d254d3c01beb894f06652cd98515c6af.poster.avif?t=1762783541\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384200/extras/d254d3c01beb894f06652cd98515c6af.webm?t=1762783541\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/384200/extras/d254d3c01beb894f06652cd98515c6af.mp4?t=1762783541\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
